'''波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納國家和大學圖書館'''（NUBBiH，''Nacionalna i univerzitetska biblioteka Bosne i Hercegovine''）是[[波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納|波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納]]的國家圖書館，位於[[塞拉耶佛|塞拉耶佛]]。圖書館修建於1891年，是[[奧匈帝國|奧匈帝國]]統治時期塞拉耶佛規模最大且最具代表性的建築物，當時曾是市政廳<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vijecnica.ba/ |title=Sarajevo Library |access-date=2015-01-09 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410225738/https://www.vijecnica.ba/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.visitsarajevo.ba/sightseeing/attractions/historical-sarajevo/vijecnica-city-hall/ Sarajevo Vijećnica] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910143821/http://www.visitsarajevo.ba/sightseeing/attractions/historical-sarajevo/vijecnica-city-hall/ |date=2011-09-10 }}</ref>。波赫戰爭期間圖書館嚴重被毀。2014年5月9日，圖書館重新開放<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oslobodjenje.ba/vijesti/sarajevo/obustava-saobracaja-povodom-otvaranja-vijecnice |title=www.oslobodjenje.ba/ Opening of the national library. |access-date=2015-01-09 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023730/http://www.oslobodjenje.ba/vijesti/sarajevo/obustava-saobracaja-povodom-otvaranja-vijecnice |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

